query:
SELECT c.id, c.gestanteId, c.dataConsulta, c.peso, c.pressaoArterial, c.alturaUterina, c.bcf, c.mf, c.observacoes, g.nome 
FROM consultasPrenatal c 
JOIN gestantes g ON c.gestanteId = g.id 
WHERE g.nome LIKE '%Graziela%Mazoni%' 
ORDER BY c.dataConsulta DESC;
